<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.8">
<l>mācuṭai yuṭampoṭu talaiyulaṟi vāyppuram veḷuttoru pōtumuṇṭu</l>
<l>tēcuṭai tiṟaluṭaik kāmatēvā nōṟkiṉṟa nōṉpiṉaik kuṟikkoḷkaṇṭāy</l>
<l>pēcuva toṉṟuṇṭiṅ kemperumāṉ peṇmaiyait talaiyuṭait tākkumvaṇṇam</l>
<l>kēcava nampiyaik kālpiṭippā ḷeṉṉumip pēṟeṉak karuḷukaṇṭāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O lustrous, valourous lord Kāma! See, understand the austerity that [I] perform</l>
<l>with a dirty body, unkempt hair, paling lips, and eating but once [a day]!</l>
<l>There is one thing that [I] need to say here, O lord: see, grace me with this good fortune</l>
<l>of [being] a woman who holds the feet of Lord Kesava</l>
<l rend="indent">in such a way that [her] womanliness is exalted!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
